metadata.name: Where It All Began
metadata.description:
Every journey comes with a beginning. Some are bright and full of hope but some, are dark and evoke every curiosity. 

This is where it all started. The one that draws all purposes. The one that will shown the real AP00.

_

Somewhere in the future, the city where the rebels belong was attacked by the rulers. They take everything from the rebels, and killed everyone. Any living being are nowhere to be found, only rustic iron and fibers lying on the ground.

Thus a little boy survive. Holding on a dear skull that he found on his path, the one thing that keep him close to his human side.

This is a story about the future, where a new type of human breed are lost and helpless. Because they're far from the truth. This is a journey where AP00 and all of his friends fighting to find the truth.
